{
  "stem": "11167.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The German-- the Russian people that was from Moscow when they start to-- to-- to get on defeat, the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew that it will come to an end.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's every day they took another town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took this town and that town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We did know that is going to be maybe end of the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We knew [? that ?] [? there ?] [? was ?] concentration camps in-- in-- in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We knew exactly, because everyone who came from the Russian Army, you know, they used to be sick-- shot in the leg-- shot in this.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They used to be in the hospitals.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And thousands of them-- thousands-- millions used to come without legs-- without their hands.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Russians--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The hospitals in--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in Uzbeskistan, because you couldn't put them in another one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There, it was quiet, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- you didn't have the bombs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You didn't have the-- then they did say, ooh, you don't know what's going on?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You're lucky that you're here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They burned the people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The burned the people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It's-- they burned the people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, they didn't-- they couldn't explain to-- what they meant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we knew this was a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Everyone-- the ones that came, a Jewish soldier, they  would say, don't ask what's going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's-- they-- it's-- it's a place where by the thousands they were burning the Jewish people in thousands-- in thousands.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then start already going more and more to the borders.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then the war was finished.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We still didn't know where we belonged-- where we were going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we-- we didn't know nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The war was finished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember the night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were celebrating.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We knew we haven't got nothing to celebrate.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
